# Virgil — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of Virgil](virgil.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit portrait): virgil.tiff -->

**what —** Dante's guide through Hell and Purgatory — reason itself, given a voice.

**why —** Sent by Beatrice to lead a living soul as far as reason can go.

**how —** With calm authority — and the quiet grief of a virtuous pagan who cannot follow to Heaven.

**where —** He dwells in Limbo, and walks the pilgrim down and up.

